  "title": "WSH Coordinator (LTA/Tunnelling, 6 days)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with Workplace Safety and Health (WSH) and Environmental Control regulations on site.</li>\n  <li>Implement, monitor, and enforce safety protocols in line with the Workplace Health and Safety Act.</li>\n  <li>Conduct regular site inspections, address safety issues, and enforce corrective actions when needed.</li>\n  <li>Maintain safety reports and documentation and perform daily safety checks.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Advanced Certificate in WSH or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>At least 3 years of experience in <strong>tunnelling</strong> in <strong>LTA projects</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Good knowledge of WSH Act and safety regulations.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701<br>\nRegistration: R1326740</p>",
